'''Nautag d'al' Gargan II''' was an [[Askajian/Legends|Askajian]], the [[Gargan family|son]] of [[Nautag d'al' Gargan|Nautag]] and [[Yarna d'al' Gargan/Legends|Yarna d'al' Gargan]] and brother of [[Luka d'al' Gargan|Luka]] and [[Leia d'al' Gargan]]. He was named after his father who died trying to prevent his family's enslavement by [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]].

He formed a [[Jizz/Legends|jizz]] trio with his siblings in the vein of [[Max Rebo/Legends|Max Rebo]].

